ğŸ§± Overview

This service enables generation of customized QR codes, with optional branding and preview, embedded as a dynamic UI (popup/modal) inside a parent application.
	â€¢	Backend: Spring Boot
	â€¢	Frontend: React (hosted separately or embedded)
	â€¢	Integration: Popup in parent app with JWT-based session
	â€¢	Deployment: Modular UI + API microservice

