ğŸ–¼ï¸ Architecture Diagram

+------------------------+       +---------------------------+       +---------------------------+
|   Parent Web App       | <---> |   QR Code UI (React)      | <---> |  QR Code API (Spring Boot)|
| (User Logged In + JWT) |       |   (Popup/iframe UI)       |       |   /api/qrcode/generate    |
+------------------------+       +---------------------------+       +---------------------------+

	â€¢	JWT passed from Parent Web App â†’ QR UI
	â€¢	QR UI communicates securely with Spring Boot APIs
	â€¢	QR generation happens server-side with ZXing, returning base64 or file

