ğŸ§ª Testing Scenarios
	â€¢	Valid JWT with form data â†’ returns QR code
	â€¢	Expired/missing JWT â†’ 401 error
	â€¢	Custom header/footer rendering
	â€¢	Uploading large files rejected with 50MB max

